ProgressBar-Stack-Renderers

This module provides enhanced renderer for the ProgressBar::Stack module. 

The new renderer provides a spinner sprite for better feedback during very 
slow operations and some means to print scrolling log-like messages without 
producing visual garbage.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc ProgressBar::Stack::Renderers

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=ProgressBar-Stack-Renderers

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/ProgressBar-Stack-Renderers

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/ProgressBar-Stack-Renderers

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/ProgressBar-Stack-Renderers/


